![](11_項目応答理論とラッシュモデル_files/figure-html/icc-plot-3.png){width=2700}
:::

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](11_項目応答理論とラッシュモデル_files/figure-html/icc-plot-4.png){width=2700}
:::

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](11_項目応答理論とラッシュモデル_files/figure-html/icc-plot-5.png){width=2700}
:::
